			"special_bonus_attack_damage_90"		"Damage talent is great for snowballing and brawling, but you won't need it in a sence that you're going to be more of an utility hero anyway and you don't have a good way to make this attack damage work"
			"special_bonus_evasion_12"		"Evasion isn't really that good by itself, but it helps with all this tanking theme and forces enemies to either buy anti-evasion items, try to kill you longer or just ignore you"
			"special_bonus_unique_dark_seer_3"		"Turns you into fight-resetter since you can make your whole team surged and retreat without losing anyone to reposition and regroup"
			"special_bonus_unique_dark_seer_4"		"It's not that good in a sence that people are already either avoiding the wall or just dying to it. Getting another wall won't make a difference most of the time"
			"special_bonus_unique_dark_seer"		"More than doubles Ion Shell damage and turns fighting against it into a nightmare: low cooldown and ridiculous magic damage all over around"
